ansible tower support only OSes include Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.7+, CentOS Linux 7.7+, and CentOS Stream 8.
to install it :
# wget https://releases.ansible.com/ansible-tower/setup/ansible-tower-setup-latest.tar.gz
# tar xfv ansible-tower-setup-latest.tar.gz 
# cd ansible-tower-setup-3.8.6-2/
# vim inventory
add the password : 04 passwords
# sudo ./setup.sh